p: The SMB-recovered ZIKV isolate TS17-2016 was passaged in C6/36 cells 4 times yielding 50% tissue culture infectious dose (TCID 50) viral titers of 6.80, 9.15, 9.80 and 8.00 log 10 TCID 50/mL for passages 1, 2, 3 and 4, respectively. The mean±SD titer of the positive mosquito pools was 3.47±0.67 log 10 TCID 50/mL. The SMB viral titers were below the TCID 50 assay threshold of detection.
